comments: Satoransky (CHI) moves laterally into Siakam's (TOR) body at the start of the drive and affects his SQBR.
Gafford (CHI) sets the pick in Siakam's (TOR) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Powell (TOR) makes marginal contact with Valentine (CHI) as he disengages from the contact.
Valentine (CHI) absorbs the contact and legally contests Powell's (TOR) driving shot attempt.
Anunoby (TOR) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact from Gafford (CHI) during his driving shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) makes marginal contact with Gafford's (CHI) upper body that does not affect his shot attempt near the rim.
Lowry (TOR) drives through Gafford's (CHI) body, who maintains a legal guarding position, and dislodges him at the end of his drive.
Markkanen (CHI) makes marginal contact with Lowry (TOR) as he disengages from the pick.
Gasol (TOR) cleanly blocks Markkanen's (CHI) shot attempt prior to making incidental body contact.
Gasol (TOR) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Markkanen (CHI) makes marginal contact with Lowry's (TOR) body during his drive.
Valentine (CHI) collapses his arm to his body and absorbs the contact from Lowry (TOR) prior to making incidental contact with Lowry's hand after his release.
LaVine (CHI) shuffles his feet after gathering the ball and before starting his dribble.
Powell (TOR) briefly grasps LaVine (CHI) during the inbound but he does not prevent LaVine from getting to the pass.
Powell (TOR) makes marginal contact with LaVine's (CHI) body as Powell disengages from the contact during the driving shot attempt.
Gasol (TOR) jumps in a legal guarding position and absorbs contact from LaVine (CHI) during the driving shot attempt.
Lowry (TOR) makes marginal body contact with Gafford (CHI) as he moves toward the loose ball.
Markkanen (CHI) makes contact with the ball before making incidental contact with Powell's (TOR) arm during the loose ball situation.
